=== ZERO_GRAVITY_DEBRIS ===
# id: 41
# title: The Zero-G Debris Field
# chinese_title: 零重力碎片
# category: Hazard
# mode: dungeon

Gravity generators have failed in this section, and shattered equipment floats in a slowly spinning cloud of debris. Sharp metal fragments tumble through the air like a slow-motion blender. Your objective lies on the far side of this deadly ballet.

* [Navigate through the debris carefully]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "浮" (fú) — to float
* [Use magnetic boots to walk along the wall]
  ~ gain_radical("力")
  "力" (lì) — force, power
* [Push through quickly, accepting some hits]
  ~ damage(7)
  "冲" (chōng) — to rush, to charge
